_header: In what order or what degree
_description: John Audelay, ‘ffac ad quod venisti’, — eight 5-line stanzas(ababc) with ‘I say algate’ refrain and burden: ‘Hit is the best erele & late / Vche mon kepe his oune state’

BodDou302.First Lines:
In wat order or what degreHole cherche haþ bownd þe
                    to…
BodDou302.Last Lines:
…Wos euer he chomys he wyl be schentI say al gate vt
                        supra
